text: Nathan Adam Sowter (born 12 October 1992 in Penrith, New South Wales, Australia) is an Australian-born English cricketer. A leg spinner, he made his debut for Middlesex in a T20 match in May 2015,http://www.espncricinfo.com/australia/content/player/747315.html taking 2 wickets for 2 runs in the 4 balls he delivered.http://www.espncricinfo.com/ci/engine/match/804485.html He made his first-class debut for Middlesex in the 2017 County Championship on 6 August 2017. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Australian cricketers Category:Middlesex cricketers Category:English cricketers Category:Australian emigrants to the United Kingdom
